  "reviews": [
    {
      "text": "Highly recommend, Josh gave our heating system a complete overhaul replacing all our radiators, flushing out the system (which was in a right state) and fitting a Hive system thermostat.\n\nJosh was honest, prompt and very well priced! Which I think is rare nowadays, he could have let us spend much more money on a combi boiler which just wouldn’t have been suitable for our property, but gave us his honest opinion and saved £££’s pounds.\n\nIf you want a plumber that actually turns up, does a good job and reasonably priced, then Josh is the man!\n\n10/10 from the Stevens household.",
      "reviewer": "Hayley",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Josh is worth his weight in gold. I contacted him, he replied instantly and kindly came to have a look the very next morning. He ordered, collected and carefully installed a beautiful new rain shower, so fast! Highly rate and recommend, thank you! 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟",
      "reviewer": "Camille",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "I can’t recommend Josh highly enough. He saved us recently on two separate occasions with emergency plumbing issues that occurred in the night. Both times he was able to come the very next day and sort it for us. Lovely chap and a great plumber.",
      "reviewer": "Martin",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "Highly recommend Josh. Fixed my salon sink super fast and is a lovely chap too!",
      "reviewer": "jessamy",
      "rating": 5
    },
    {
      "text": "I contacted Josh this morning as I had a problem with water pouring out of a pipe that hadn’t been capped off properly and although just back from holidays came sorted for me quickly and efficiently.  I can’t thank him enough can recommend him to anyone and any future work I will give to him 100%",
      "reviewer": "Glenda",
      "rating": 4
    }
  ],
